b53ad60c50f4db9028e06ebd5da541a6b874","tid":2034770,"uid":75692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T15:27:15.000Z","msg":"startup都用node 或者go啦<br />\n遲d實多埋deno<br />\nruby都好似沒落緊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T01:11:52.000Z","msg":"Node.js 啲 ORM 好廢，一係全玩 Serverless + DynamoDB + event sourcing"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T04:53:17.000Z","msg":"TypeORM: 我屌你老母啊"},{"pid":"a9d55beed67f147e3c7160b1e3ffd3d580b0b38d","tid":2034770,"uid":81716,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T05:17:06.000Z","msg":"如果俾我揀 startup 用自己最順手既language 就夠，能夠以最快速度deliver 到舊野出黎係start up 生存模式<br />\n<br />\n當有第一筆錢番黎之後再花時間revamp , 講效能講執行速度到極致，就追求C++, C, Rust ，呢三款都無GC 要你自己deallocate pointer memory , pointer 周圍飛黎飛去，無番咁上下data structure 會好難寫得好，而且仲要細心花時間, 呢個level 可以少用library 就減少用，盡量減低自己既心理負擔<br />\n<br />\n講請人難易度加上高開發效率，但對執行速度無咁執著，bottleneck 無咁高既就諗python, php , ror, java, nodejs...etc modern language 橫掂又唔洗個舊野咁快，隨便用一隻就ok ，分析下個language 擅長邊個領域、所以呢個level 關注既點係生態framework 做輪子，極速上手各種library framework 就最好<br />\n<br />\n我自己係建議用GO + react or vue，盡量減低心理負擔 keep KISS ( keep it simple and stupid)"},{"pid":"c4f1162d12c2d9d5c998259a888aff9bc707c297","tid":2034770,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2dd87f2eb331f67093effc7e28ec33fdf7572350","tid":2034770,"uid":279606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ed37486a803f08923379f67d91053cb10c124b3","tid":2034770,"uid":125976,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"200bb53ad60c50f4db9028e06ebd5da541a6b874","tid":2034770,"uid":75692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T15:27:15.000Z","msg":"startup都用node 或者go啦<br />\n遲d實多埋deno<br />\nruby都好似沒落緊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T01:11:52.000Z","msg":"Node.js 啲 ORM 好廢，一係全玩 Serverless + DynamoDB + event sourcing"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T04:53:17.000Z","msg":"TypeORM: 我屌你老母啊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T05:25:18.000Z","msg":"仲廢過 sequelize<img src=\"/assets/faces